{{Top|leg}}
'''Jo trees''' were plants native to [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. Florists in local areas such as [[Gadrin]] often used jo cuttings in their arrangements. [[Caarite]]s had a reaction to jo trees, becoming uncomfortable in proximity to jo cuttings. Some Caarites, such as [[Jyll Xon]], had more severe allergic reactions, passing out and going into convulsions if they sniffed an arrangement containing jo clippings. Fortunately, these reactions were not life threatening.

